name: Zach Ertz
bio: Believer. Husband to @julieertz. Super Bowl Champion!  Co-founder of @ertzfamilyfoundation . business inquiries contact steve@caricsports.com

social_posts.post_text:
I am Honored to be the Arizona Cardinals nominee for the Walter Payton Man of the Year.  Julie and I strive to make a significant impact in the communities that we play in and we understand this nomination would not be possible without the incredible help of those who support the @ertzfamilyfoundation in many significant ways.

While this is amazing affirmation of the work we have done so far, we look forward to the completion of the House of Hope in Philadelphia and to continue to address food insecurity in Arizona. The best is yet to come!
